<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV96">
<l>varampilāta māyamāya. vaiyamēḻu meymmaiyē</l>
<l>varampilūḻi yēttilumva rampilāta kīrttiyāy</l>
<l>varampilāta palpiṟappa ṟuttuvantu niṉkaḻal</l>
<l>poruntumāti runtanīva rañceypuṇṭa rīkaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You with boundless wonders! O wonderful Lord! O You whose glories are infinite</l>
<l>Even if [the people of] all seven worlds truly praise [You] for countless aeons!</l>
<l>O lotus[-eyed Lord]! Grant me properly the means to come and abide</l>
<l>At Your feet, severing the many, countless births!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
